{"tid":909020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大中學教歷史掛旭日旗　韓裔學生抗議獲近萬人支持　校方終除旗","createTime":"2018-11-20T04:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T05:36:59.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1dabb6e1de2fe7f697b2304b0df708958be143f","tid":909020,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181120/s00005/d34102aed1044c3e6ff7a36d8ec6b02d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181120%2Fs00005%2Fd34102aed1044c3e6ff7a36d8ec6b02d.jpg&h=7a6f2d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大卑詩省蘭里市一間中學的課室，懸掛二戰期間象徵軍國主義的日本軍隊「旭日旗」，引發韓裔學生抗議，學生的請願獲得9799人支持，校方終應要求除下「旭日旗」。<br />\n<br />\n蘭里市沃爾納特格羅夫中學一名九年級文姓韓裔學生，前天（18日）在網上發起請願，反對歷史老師以「教學目的」為由在課室掛「旭日旗」，要求校方除下該旗幟。文表示，這面「旭日旗」讓他想起祖父母的悲慘遭遇，「難以想像有人不會發現這個符號（旭日旗）是不人道和不道德」。他又說，「旭日旗」對亞洲學生來說是「非常冒犯」，因為這令他們想起可怕的日本戰爭罪行，例如數以萬計年輕女性被迫成為性奴。<br />\n<br />\n文表示，每個人都知道希特勒及其政府犯下的反人道暴行，但是日軍的「慰安婦」、活人實驗和「南京大屠殺」都是加拿大學校沒有教授的歷史，重視程度不及納粹大屠殺，「既然納粹黨徽被禁，『旭日旗』同樣也該被禁」。<br />\n<br />\n請願最終獲得9799人支持。學校董事會發言人霍夫（Ken Hoff）回應事件稱，掛起「旭日旗」是作為歷史課話題，無意冒犯任何人，校方最終亦移除了「旭日旗」。<br />\n<br />\n(韓國時報/環球網)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181120/s00005/1542677112332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181120%2Fs00005%2F1542677112332&d=pYblX2s1qceYPLHhGbA02m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a01494df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181120%2Fs00005%2F1542677112332&h=e659ffa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181120/s00005/1542677112332</a>"},{"pid":"97b529903f97f7725cf80dc13c1a4d12ab384291","tid":909020,"uid":34666,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:42:38.000Z","msg":"大把韓國人係依枝旗下作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252855f7ee30bea311003cfdeed0ebae2406028c","tid":909020,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"個到好多韓人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be689eb1715e6dc52bdf21d368c2aff1c0af542b","tid":909020,"uid":164913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bda734a0c86273b9779d46884b8f6e232b675fc8","tid":909020,"uid":73613,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a4b0e499243be4e215e814e6f45dbd73daa35b6","tid":909020,"uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"97b529903f97f7725cf80dc13c1a4d12ab384291","tid":909020,"uid":34666,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:42:38.000Z","msg":"大把韓國人係依枝旗下作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果時都有歷史書話臺韓籍嘅日兵特別凶狠<br />\n<br />\n反而日本本土果d就比較温和"},{"pid":"1cd0b249999b2f7b5b33b0843c43ab61d88a812b","tid":909020,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"又係泡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}